---
import LifecycleStep from "./LifecycleStep.astro";
---

<section class="lifecycle">

<h2>Vulnerability Lifecycle</h2>

<p class="intro">
Every zero-day follows a journey—from discovery by researchers to exploitation by attackers and eventually a security patch.
</p>

<div class="timeline">

<LifecycleStep
emoji="🔍"
title="Discovery"
description="A software flaw is discovered by a researcher or attacker."
/>

<div class="arrow">→</div>

<LifecycleStep
emoji="🧪"
title="Analysis"
description="The vulnerability is analyzed to understand its impact."
/>

<div class="arrow">→</div>

<LifecycleStep
emoji="💥"
title="Exploitation"
description="Attackers may create malware or exploits before a fix exists."
/>

<div class="arrow">→</div>

<LifecycleStep
emoji="📢"
title="Disclosure"
description="The issue is reported responsibly to the software vendor."
/>

<div class="arrow">→</div>

<LifecycleStep
emoji="🛠️"
title="Patch"
description="The vendor releases an update to fix the vulnerability."
/>

</div>

</section>

<style>
.lifecycle{
    padding:7rem 0;
}

.lifecycle h2{
    text-align:center;
    font-size:3rem;
    margin-bottom:1rem;
}

.intro{
    max-width:700px;
    margin:auto;
    text-align:center;
    color:#9da7b3;
    margin-bottom:4rem;
}

.timeline{
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:center;
    gap:1rem;
    flex-wrap:wrap;
}

.arrow{
    font-size:2rem;
    color:#58a6ff;
}

@media(max-width:900px){
    .arrow{
        display:none;
    }

    .timeline{
        display:grid;
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
    }
}
</style>